title: [Faeilythe's Fashions, Ensembles]
description: White-washed oak furnishings augment the deeper greys of the grainy mistwood walls, and serve to display Faeilythe's gowns and coordinates in fine fashion.  Gold sconces filled with tuberose-scented beeswax candles perfume the air and add a touch of illumination at this end of the shop.
